{"tid":894072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無屍命案 被告謀殺罪成今判終身監禁","createTime":"2018-11-08T06:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T07:04:44.000Z","uid":167451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7998a37075e3583c624682c845b746d55d9a37","tid":894072,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"深水埗前年5月發生無屍兇殺案，六旬女保安員人間蒸發，警方拘捕其胞姊的前女婿，並控以謀殺等罪。案件經過逾半個月審訊後，由四男三女組成的陪審團昨退庭商議逾9小時，終以五比二大比數裁定被告謀殺罪成，並以六比一大比數裁定他阻止屍體合法殮葬罪成，案件今日(8日)判刑，被告顏永周依例被判處終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%84%A1%E5%B1%8D%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E4%BB%8A%E5%88%A4%E7%B5%82%E8%BA%AB%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81-030711008.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25B1%258D%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25A6%2581-030711008.html&d=Ka4QYMh6GiHTsAA8ISVHEk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=f3fe20ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%84%A1%E5%B1%8D%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E4%BB%8A%E5%88%A4%E7%B5%82%E8%BA%AB%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81-030711008.html</a>"},{"pid":"a87c603d57e483649e6b01dab92ffcaed9a6333f","tid":894072,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64b98bb914cc30f93b96bea555efaf0bbefaf9e","tid":894072,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:26:51.000Z","msg":"擺到明係佢地做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 判得好"},{"pid":"d57dfe5fffbe6bcf98a7f2b942c642108bb294ed","tid":894072,"uid":1055